name: 20220111_Variation_Titian
description:
This NFT is minted as a special gift for Rich Nicoloff, a professional photographer, a supportive patron of NFT art and a connoisseur of Strangeness.

This drawing, based on a landscape drawing by Titian, is created while I was listening to Bach's Goldberg Variations - a „Keyboard exercise… Composed for connoisseurs, for the refreshment of their spirits…“ 

Hopefully, this little piece of drawing can serve the similar function too.

11th, January, 2022
Metamaler
